query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('boundary-value-problem',
'covariance',
'divergent-series',
'economics',
'files',
'group-actions',
'group-isomorphism',
'lagrange-multiplier',
'mysql',
'orthogonality',
'polar-coordinates',
'quantifiers',
'symmetric-groups',
'weak-convergence',
'windows-7')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Disciplined',
'Favorite Question',
'Investor',
'Peer Pressure',
'Promoter',
'Pundit',
'Self-Learner',
'Suffrage',
'Talkative',
'Tenacious') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
